{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/pages/gatsby-blog-tutorial-part-2/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"codingwbeto"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"dc11daa9-c1df-56e0-9f2b-27a49620af9c","excerpt":"In this tutorial we will do the following: Edit Homepage When you ran the Gatsby preview server, it says to edit src/pages/index.js so lets give that a tryâ€¦","html":"<p>In this tutorial we will do the following:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- Delete the congratulations message\n\n- Use normalize.css to guarantee consistency of css styling with all browsers\n\n- Create a navbar component and use bootstrap for styling</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"edit-homepage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#edit-homepage\" aria-label=\"edit homepage permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Edit Homepage</h3>\n<p>When you ran the Gatsby preview server, it says to edit src/pages/index.js so lets give that a try.</p>\n<p>Lets start off by deleting the congradulations message and the line it says to edit the src/pages/index.js file</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/codingwbeto/static/c54629316ef636d29ab2b66c17ef2c48/669cd/editingIndex.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.18987341772153%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Editing src/pages/index.js\"\n        title=\"Editing src/pages/index.js\"\n        src=\"/codingwbeto/static/c54629316ef636d29ab2b66c17ef2c48/f058b/editingIndex.png\"\n        srcset=\"/codingwbeto/static/c54629316ef636d29ab2b66c17ef2c48/c26ae/editingIndex.png 158w,\n/codingwbeto/static/c54629316ef636d29ab2b66c17ef2c48/6bdcf/editingIndex.png 315w,\n/codingwbeto/static/c54629316ef636d29ab2b66c17ef2c48/f058b/editingIndex.png 630w,\n/codingwbeto/static/c54629316ef636d29ab2b66c17ef2c48/40601/editingIndex.png 945w,\n/codingwbeto/static/c54629316ef636d29ab2b66c17ef2c48/78612/editingIndex.png 1260w,\n/codingwbeto/static/c54629316ef636d29ab2b66c17ef2c48/669cd/editingIndex.png 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"navbar-component\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#navbar-component\" aria-label=\"navbar component permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Navbar component</h3>\n<p>Lets go ahead and add a navbar</p>\n<p>Create file src/components/Navbar.js</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/codingwbeto/static/9a07ae22fda002344d3281a8f4f56c7b/6660b/navComponentArrowFunction.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.645569620253163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Nav Component Arrow Function\"\n        title=\"Nav Component Arrow Function\"\n        src=\"/codingwbeto/static/9a07ae22fda002344d3281a8f4f56c7b/f058b/navComponentArrowFunction.png\"\n        srcset=\"/codingwbeto/static/9a07ae22fda002344d3281a8f4f56c7b/c26ae/navComponentArrowFunction.png 158w,\n/codingwbeto/static/9a07ae22fda002344d3281a8f4f56c7b/6bdcf/navComponentArrowFunction.png 315w,\n/codingwbeto/static/9a07ae22fda002344d3281a8f4f56c7b/f058b/navComponentArrowFunction.png 630w,\n/codingwbeto/static/9a07ae22fda002344d3281a8f4f56c7b/40601/navComponentArrowFunction.png 945w,\n/codingwbeto/static/9a07ae22fda002344d3281a8f4f56c7b/78612/navComponentArrowFunction.png 1260w,\n/codingwbeto/static/9a07ae22fda002344d3281a8f4f56c7b/6660b/navComponentArrowFunction.png 2278w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I sprinkled some bootstrap to quickly style this Nav component, create a file called gatsby-browser.js in the root folder of your project. Here is were you import your css. It is best practice to always use normalize.css because diffrent browsers interpret styling in there own ways and this makes sure your styling is consitant in every browser.</p>\n<h3 id=\"install-bootstrap-and-normalize\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#install-bootstrap-and-normalize\" aria-label=\"install bootstrap and normalize permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install bootstrap and normalize</h3>\n<p>To get bootstrap just install it using <code class=\"language-text\">npm install bootstrap</code></p>\n<p>To get normalize.css just install it using <code class=\"language-text\">npm install normalize.css</code></p>\n<p>Import them inside <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-browser.js</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/codingwbeto/static/eb64abfd2937e87f16e85a4898b3afae/5fada/gatsby-browser.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.11392405063291%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Gatsby Browser Page\"\n        title=\"Gatsby Browser Page\"\n        src=\"/codingwbeto/static/eb64abfd2937e87f16e85a4898b3afae/f058b/gatsby-browser.png\"\n        srcset=\"/codingwbeto/static/eb64abfd2937e87f16e85a4898b3afae/c26ae/gatsby-browser.png 158w,\n/codingwbeto/static/eb64abfd2937e87f16e85a4898b3afae/6bdcf/gatsby-browser.png 315w,\n/codingwbeto/static/eb64abfd2937e87f16e85a4898b3afae/f058b/gatsby-browser.png 630w,\n/codingwbeto/static/eb64abfd2937e87f16e85a4898b3afae/40601/gatsby-browser.png 945w,\n/codingwbeto/static/eb64abfd2937e87f16e85a4898b3afae/78612/gatsby-browser.png 1260w,\n/codingwbeto/static/eb64abfd2937e87f16e85a4898b3afae/5fada/gatsby-browser.png 1706w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"importing-our-navbar\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#importing-our-navbar\" aria-label=\"importing our navbar permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Importing our navbar</h3>\n<p>Lets import this component into our homepage <code class=\"language-text\">src/pages/index.js</code></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/codingwbeto/static/3c618844eb5f78ce6a68ecd964934ee5/5522e/importingNav.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.37974683544304%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Importing Nav\"\n        title=\"Importing Nav\"\n        src=\"/codingwbeto/static/3c618844eb5f78ce6a68ecd964934ee5/f058b/importingNav.png\"\n        srcset=\"/codingwbeto/static/3c618844eb5f78ce6a68ecd964934ee5/c26ae/importingNav.png 158w,\n/codingwbeto/static/3c618844eb5f78ce6a68ecd964934ee5/6bdcf/importingNav.png 315w,\n/codingwbeto/static/3c618844eb5f78ce6a68ecd964934ee5/f058b/importingNav.png 630w,\n/codingwbeto/static/3c618844eb5f78ce6a68ecd964934ee5/40601/importingNav.png 945w,\n/codingwbeto/static/3c618844eb5f78ce6a68ecd964934ee5/78612/importingNav.png 1260w,\n/codingwbeto/static/3c618844eb5f78ce6a68ecd964934ee5/5522e/importingNav.png 2680w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Your page should now look like this</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/codingwbeto/static/fac13ecd4e440d8692bc98b18bb7f5ca/669cd/previewNav.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.65822784810127%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Preview Nav\"\n        title=\"Preview Nav\"\n        src=\"/codingwbeto/static/fac13ecd4e440d8692bc98b18bb7f5ca/f058b/previewNav.png\"\n        srcset=\"/codingwbeto/static/fac13ecd4e440d8692bc98b18bb7f5ca/c26ae/previewNav.png 158w,\n/codingwbeto/static/fac13ecd4e440d8692bc98b18bb7f5ca/6bdcf/previewNav.png 315w,\n/codingwbeto/static/fac13ecd4e440d8692bc98b18bb7f5ca/f058b/previewNav.png 630w,\n/codingwbeto/static/fac13ecd4e440d8692bc98b18bb7f5ca/40601/previewNav.png 945w,\n/codingwbeto/static/fac13ecd4e440d8692bc98b18bb7f5ca/78612/previewNav.png 1260w,\n/codingwbeto/static/fac13ecd4e440d8692bc98b18bb7f5ca/669cd/previewNav.png 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby blog tutorial part 2","date":"September 19, 2015","description":"Tutorial to learn how to edit the homepage"},"headings":[{"value":"Edit Homepage","depth":3},{"value":"Navbar component","depth":3},{"value":"Install bootstrap and normalize","depth":3},{"value":"Importing our navbar","depth":3}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/pages/gatsby-blog-tutorial-part-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby blog tutorial part 1"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/pages/web-development-tips/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Web Development Tips"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"dc11daa9-c1df-56e0-9f2b-27a49620af9c","previousPostId":"87af7389-1c21-5638-8e2e-7d3f23106efb","nextPostId":"8753638f-472b-50db-88d6-2d00fcaf179e"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}